---
title: Thai-Spiced Beef with Dressed Veggies
description: Beef seasoned with ginger and Thai-style spices get thinly sliced and served atop a bowl full of fluffy basmati rice for tonight's delicious dinner! We've added marinated cucumbers and shredded carrots, and green onions for extra flavour and freshness.
